3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper formulates geometric model fitting as a mode seeking problem on a hypergraph, which involves graph-based algorithms and data structures. 
4. cs.CG (Computational Geometry): The paper deals with geometric model fitting, which is a subfield of computational geometry.
